===Population===
According to the 2020 census, there were 897 people in Gloster. As of the [[census]]<ref name="GR2">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]] |accessdate=January 31, 2008 |title=U.S. Census website }}</ref> of 2010, there were 960 people, 223 households, and 114 families residing in the town.

